### Decision triggers (commit to these now, not in the moment)
- [ ] If base-case runway falls below 6 months: raise / cut / pivot — decide which.
- [ ] If actuals track the Worst scenario for **2 consecutive months**: switch operating plan to Worst (cut variable burn, freeze hiring).
- [ ] If actuals exceed Optimistic for **2 consecutive months**: invest aggressively (hire, marketing).
- [ ] Refresh this table monthly with actuals; compare prior forecast vs. actual to calibrate.

